#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:2 580c00801da4442599c6e3079cdd94be
msgid "Contributing"
msgstr "贡献指南"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:4 e8604de8f0814a2ba817099bfe4dfa59
msgid ""
"TensorMesh is small enough that one well-aimed patch can move the needle. "
"This page covers the practical loop: get a dev environment, run the tests, "
"build the docs, and open a PR."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 规模不大，一个有的放矢的补丁就足以带来切实改变。本页介绍实际的工作流程：搭建开发环境、运行测试、构建文档，以及提交 PR。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:8 a3a7569c23ce4e54a848174e6274ee14
msgid ""
"If you have an idea but aren't sure where it fits, post on "
":doc:`github_discussions` (*Ideas & RFCs* category) or drop a line on "
":doc:`discord`. For confirmed bugs and specific feature requests, the issue "
"tracker is the right entry point — see :doc:`github_issues`."
msgstr ""
"如果您有想法但不确定它该归在何处，可在 :doc:`github_discussions`\\ （\\ *Ideas & RFCs* 类别）中发帖，或在"
" :doc:`discord` 上留言。对于已确认的缺陷和具体的功能请求，issue 跟踪器才是合适的入口——参见 "
":doc:`github_issues`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:15 38b39295f13643339cfbdf6c931e3e15
msgid "Getting set up"
msgstr "环境搭建"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:17 0c668a2b02bf4e90a91e1d4eda318064
msgid "Requirements:"
msgstr "环境要求："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:19 f03f2cfba53247fdbb03f01411a0f8d5
msgid "**Python ≥ 3.10**"
msgstr "**Python ≥ 3.10**"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:20 64df12a9b2404230afe66404484f9bd0
msgid "**PyTorch ≥ 2.0** (with CUDA if you want to run the GPU paths)"
msgstr "**PyTorch ≥ 2.0**\\ （若要运行 GPU 路径，则需带 CUDA）"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:22 98bf2048a9bc4519bb3f442f62dc8125
msgid ""
"Everything else installs from PyPI in the step below — including ``torch-"
"sla`` (``>= 0.2.1``), the hard dependency that provides every sparse-solver "
"backend. No C++ toolchain or manual build step is required."
msgstr ""
"其余所有依赖都可在下面的步骤中从 PyPI 安装——包括 ``torch-sla``\\ （\\ ``>= 0.2.1``\\ "
"），这是提供全部稀疏求解器后端的硬性依赖。无需 C++ 工具链或手动构建步骤。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:27 c96e93b5fec844d2bcd21b63f0148c8b
msgid "Clone and install in editable mode:"
msgstr "克隆并以可编辑模式安装："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:35 867286bf62ca4b9fbc63a078599d591a
msgid ""
"Optional extras: ``cupy`` / ``cudss`` (GPU sparse-direct solver backends), "
"``gpu`` (both at once), and ``example`` (Plotly for some figure scripts)."
msgstr ""
"可选附加项：\\ ``cupy`` / ``cudss``\\ （GPU 稀疏直接求解器后端）、\\ ``gpu``\\ （同时安装两者），以及 "
"``example``\\ （部分绘图脚本所需的 Plotly）。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:39 e28a2effcc1b41f49fbdbea1dee9161a
msgid ""
"Smoke-test the install by running the bundled checker, which solves a tiny "
"Poisson problem on CPU (and on GPU if available) and reports which sparse-"
"solver backends are wired up:"
msgstr ""
"运行随附的检查脚本对安装进行冒烟测试，它会在 CPU 上（以及在可用时在 GPU 上）求解一个极小的泊松方程问题，并报告哪些稀疏求解器后端已就绪："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:47 4e159cff29284c85a87983eebf3e786f
msgid ""
"If both the CPU and the CUDA solve print sensible errors against the "
"analytical reference, you're good."
msgstr "如果 CPU 和 CUDA 两种求解相对于解析参考解都打印出合理的误差，那就说明一切正常。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:52 3c277b711b594ad29ba693b4a31edc78
msgid "Running the tests"
msgstr "运行测试"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:54 865175c2aba0481aacb1cdf537f1393d
msgid ""
"Tests live under ``tests/``, mirroring the package layout "
"(``tests/element/``, ``tests/sparse/``, ``tests/ode/``, …). They use plain "
"pytest:"
msgstr ""
"测试位于 ``tests/`` 目录下，其结构与包的布局相对应（\\ ``tests/element/``\\ 、\\ "
"``tests/sparse/``\\ 、\\ ``tests/ode/`` 等）。它们使用原生 pytest："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:65 4a4dadd25f95450697057d21588b936c
msgid "A few conventions worth knowing before writing new tests:"
msgstr "在编写新测试之前，有几条值得了解的约定："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:67 4e8ad1b01f63414eb651d0ad9a022112
msgid ""
"**Default to ``float64`` and ``cpu``** in new tests; add a GPU variant "
"guarded by ``@pytest.mark.skipif(not torch.cuda.is_available())`` when the "
"code path you're exercising has device/dtype handling."
msgstr ""
"**新测试中默认使用 ``float64`` 和 ``cpu``**\\ ；当您所测试的代码路径涉及设备/数据类型的处理时，请添加由 "
"``@pytest.mark.skipif(not torch.cuda.is_available())`` 保护的 GPU 变体测试。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:70 f4486ad3bfe8436682387a0ebe19bc92
msgid ""
"**Avoid NumPy inside assembler ``forward()`` methods.** Assemblers run under"
" ``torch.vmap``, which is silently incompatible with NumPy arrays — stay in "
"torch."
msgstr ""
"**避免在装配器的 ``forward()`` 方法内部使用 NumPy。** 装配器在 ``torch.vmap`` 下运行，而它与 NumPy "
"数组存在不会报错的隐性不兼容——请始终使用 torch。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:73 7717db86825f40daac1965d35281eabd
msgid ""
"**Name tests after what they exercise**, not the file. Duplicate function "
"names across test files run fine but make ``pytest -k`` filtering noisy."
msgstr ""
"**测试的命名应反映其所测试的内容**\\ ，而非文件名。在不同测试文件中重复的函数名虽然能正常运行，却会使 ``pytest -k`` 过滤变得混乱。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:79 9574fb989a434de3b0e1d9ccb2d7f718
msgid "Building the docs"
msgstr "构建文档"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:81 f654df4c3f8a4f6d9c9b0dc89a917de0
msgid "The docs use Sphinx with the ``pydata_sphinx_theme``. Build locally:"
msgstr "文档使用 Sphinx 配合 ``pydata_sphinx_theme`` 主题。在本地构建："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:88 93498defe6ab4485a5790b7e80f6ca86
msgid ""
"Rendered output goes to ``docs/_build/html/``; open "
"``docs/_build/html/index.html`` to view. A clean build currently emits a "
"handful of pre-existing warnings — a stale ``ExplicitRungeKutta`` cross-"
"reference in ``example_gallery/wave.rst`` plus a few NumPy-style docstring-"
"formatting warnings — so the working rule is simply: don't add new ones, and"
" fixing an existing one is always welcome."
msgstr ""
"渲染输出会生成到 ``docs/_build/html/``\\ ；打开 ``docs/_build/html/index.html`` "
"即可查看。目前即使是干净的构建也会产生少量已存在的警告——``example_gallery/wave.rst`` 中一个过时的 "
"``ExplicitRungeKutta`` 交叉引用，外加几处 NumPy "
"风格的文档字符串格式警告——因此实际的规则很简单：不要新增警告，而修复已有的警告则始终受欢迎。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:95 b44d1c3a2bd24eae9a54c1a8949f9b5b
msgid ""
"The site is **bilingual EN/ZH** via Sphinx's gettext workflow. The canonical"
" English source is the ``.rst`` files; Chinese strings live in ``.po`` files"
" under ``docs/source/locale/zh_CN/``. To regenerate the ``.po`` after "
"editing English text:"
msgstr ""
"本站点通过 Sphinx 的 gettext 工作流实现\\ **中英双语**\\ 。权威的英文源是 ``.rst`` 文件；中文字符串位于 "
"``docs/source/locale/zh_CN/`` 下的 ``.po`` 文件中。在编辑英文文本后，重新生成 ``.po`` 文件："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:105
#: 52f8ebd6c500436aa1ff95a67b16571f
msgid "To build the Chinese site or both sites together:"
msgstr "构建中文站点，或同时构建两个站点："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:112
#: d0a6f7ffbeab4a49a243bec173ad97a3
msgid ""
"If your PR only touches English text, you can leave the ``.po`` files alone "
"— a maintainer will batch the i18n update."
msgstr "如果您的 PR 仅改动英文文本，可以不去动 ``.po`` 文件——维护者会批量处理国际化更新。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:117
#: e1504848399d402a9ca6ac567a3d0dca
msgid "Code style"
msgstr "代码风格"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:119
#: ab243ba880504de3bf1784f1927d7dd6
msgid ""
"There is no automated formatter / linter enforced in CI today, so the "
"working rule is **match the file you're editing**. In practice that means:"
msgstr "目前 CI 中没有强制执行的自动格式化工具或代码检查工具，因此实际的规则是\\ **与您正在编辑的文件保持一致**\\ 。具体而言，这意味着："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:123
#: 311ccde8a08f4630bf82e7653732dea6
msgid "4-space indent, PEP 8 in spirit, line length around 88-100 characters."
msgstr "采用 4 个空格缩进，遵循 PEP 8 的精神，行长约为 88 至 100 个字符。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:124
#: e476b0b2d8c347bbb89c452913a964f2
msgid ""
"**NumPy-style docstrings** with Summary → Parameters → Returns → Notes → "
"Examples (in that order). Type hints are encouraged but not required; if you"
" add them, prefer ``torch.Tensor`` over the generic ``Any``."
msgstr ""
"**NumPy 风格的文档字符串**\\ ，依次为 Summary → Parameters → Returns → Notes → "
"Examples（按此顺序）。鼓励但不强制使用类型注解；如果您添加注解，请优先使用 ``torch.Tensor`` 而非泛型的 ``Any``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:128
#: 9b317bfedcc148909e44bb9d11b1ff78
msgid ""
"Use the existing **``BufferDict`` / ``BufferList``** containers "
"(``tensormesh.nn``) for ``nn.Module``-compatible tensor collections. Don't "
"roll a plain ``dict`` of tensors when crossing ``nn.Module`` boundaries."
msgstr ""
"对于与 ``nn.Module`` 兼容的张量集合，请使用已有的 **``BufferDict`` / ``BufferList``** 容器（\\ "
"``tensormesh.nn``\\ ）。在跨越 ``nn.Module`` 边界时，不要自行使用普通的张量 ``dict``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:132
#: 6794ba6678f94b6390452ccc29277f39
msgid ""
"Keep ``forward()`` methods pure tensor code — no Python control flow on "
"tensor values, no NumPy, no ``.item()`` calls unless the result is for a "
"print/log."
msgstr ""
"请让 ``forward()`` 方法保持为纯张量代码——不要基于张量值进行 Python 控制流操作，不要使用 "
"NumPy，除非结果用于打印/日志，否则不要调用 ``.item()``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:138
#: b508fdc2667c420380651ab4c0a44aa6
msgid "Submitting a pull request"
msgstr "提交拉取请求"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:140
#: c89e1b1288a64017b0a2af1ff74d5878
msgid "The mechanical flow:"
msgstr "具体操作流程："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:142
#: 03dc92280471418b83c832a6606f4815
msgid ""
"**Fork & branch from ``main``.** Branch naming is informal; ``feat/<short>``"
" / ``fix/<short>`` / ``docs/<short>`` matches the commit-message style."
msgstr ""
"**从 ``main`` 派生并创建分支。** 分支命名不拘形式；\\ ``feat/<short>`` / ``fix/<short>`` / "
"``docs/<short>`` 与提交信息的风格相匹配。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:144
#: a80494c44be04d499e82ff6c30a045f4
msgid ""
"**Write tests.** A PR that touches numerical code without an associated test"
" is unlikely to be merged. CPU + ``float64`` is the minimum; add a GPU "
"variant if the touched code branches on device."
msgstr ""
"**编写测试。** 改动数值代码却没有相应测试的 PR 不太可能被合并。CPU + ``float64`` "
"是最低要求；如果所改动的代码会根据设备分支，请添加一个 GPU 变体测试。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:147
#: d07d780bd0fb4e61825982c784a25355
msgid ""
"**Run the relevant tests and a docs build** locally; both should be clean."
msgstr "在本地\\ **运行相关测试并构建一次文档**\\ ；两者都应没有问题。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:149
#: 604f91bb02d946a08c2cf64cf3aa8f2a
msgid ""
"**Open the PR**, link the issue with ``Fixes #NN`` (or ``Refs #NN`` for "
"partial fixes), and fill in the body explaining the *why* — not just the "
"*what*, since the diff already covers that."
msgstr ""
"**提交 PR**\\ ，用 ``Fixes #NN`` 关联对应 issue（部分修复则用 ``Refs #NN``\\ ），并在正文中说明\\ "
"*为什么*\\ 这样做——而不仅仅是\\ *做了什么*\\ ，因为后者已由 diff 体现。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:152
#: e3e430b77fc2446ea23ebda03463ef4c
msgid ""
"**Commit message style** follows the rest of the project: ``<type>(<scope>):"
" <imperative summary>``, e.g. ``fix(ode): propagate u0.dtype/device through "
"step()``. Types in use: ``feat``, ``fix``, ``docs``, ``test``, ``refactor``,"
" ``perf``, ``ci``."
msgstr ""
"**提交信息风格**\\ 沿用项目其余部分的约定：\\ ``<type>(<scope>): <imperative summary>``\\ ，例如 "
"``fix(ode): propagate u0.dtype/device through step()``\\ 。使用中的类型有：\\ "
"``feat``\\ 、\\ ``fix``\\ 、\\ ``docs``\\ 、\\ ``test``\\ 、\\ ``refactor``\\ "
"、\\ ``perf``\\ 、\\ ``ci``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:158
#: 8e0fbd7ed24d46019346a8e7c9224642
msgid "What reviewers will look for:"
msgstr "评审者会关注的要点："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:160
#: 38959466c756460fae3972111e395f61
msgid ""
"Tests that exercise the path you changed, including the failure mode before "
"your fix if applicable."
msgstr "覆盖您所改动路径的测试，并在适用时包含修复前的失败情形。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:162
#: 5f76c4a3f3d0459b9e70f4fcf2ef8161
msgid "No new Sphinx warnings if you touched docstrings or ``.rst``."
msgstr "如果您改动了文档字符串或 ``.rst`` 文件，不应引入新的 Sphinx 警告。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:163
#: 0199ad6b65fe425eb1d7abb59efc29d8
msgid ""
"No accidental backwards-incompatibility — if a public symbol is renamed or "
"removed, the PR description should call it out explicitly."
msgstr "不应出现意外的向后不兼容——如果某个公共符号被重命名或移除，PR 描述中应明确指出这一点。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:166
#: 5726eca9a04d4f8d8144c4da0f2081f3
msgid ""
"Numerical changes (new element, new quadrature, new solver) should include "
"at least one analytical-reference check."
msgstr "数值方面的改动（新增单元、新增数值积分、新增求解器）应至少包含一项对照解析参考解的检验。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:169
#: d4117237551b4f54a6ec583d5e5f4613
msgid ""
"This is a small maintainer team; response times are best-effort. If a PR has"
" been silent for more than a week or two, a polite ping on :doc:`discord` "
"``#dev`` is welcome."
msgstr ""
"这是一个小规模的维护团队；响应时间为尽力而为。如果某个 PR 沉寂了一两周以上，欢迎在 :doc:`discord` 的 ``#dev`` "
"频道礼貌地提醒一下。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:175
#: 522a4b9556464edf9ee4121d862bc9f5
msgid "Sign-off and the Developer Certificate of Origin"
msgstr "签署声明与开发者原创证书（DCO）"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:177
#: bd4203ec722346439fa57113c8fcc4e0
msgid ""
"Every commit that lands on ``main`` must be signed off under the `Developer "
"Certificate of Origin <https://developercertificate.org/>`_ (DCO) — the same"
" lightweight contribution policy used by the Linux kernel, PyTorch, vLLM, "
"and most Apache-licensed projects. The full text lives in the ``DCO`` file "
"at the repository root; the gist is that you certify the code is yours to "
"contribute (or that it came from a properly-licensed source) and that you "
"are submitting it under the project's Apache 2.0 license."
msgstr ""
"进入 ``main`` 的每一次提交都必须依据 `开发者原创证书 <https://developercertificate.org/>`_\\ "
"（DCO）进行签署声明——这与 Linux 内核、PyTorch、vLLM 以及大多数采用 Apache "
"许可的项目所使用的轻量级贡献政策相同。完整文本位于代码仓库根目录的 ``DCO`` "
"文件中；其要点是，您声明这些代码是您有权贡献的（或来自一个许可正当的来源），并且您是在本项目的 Apache 2.0 许可下提交它的。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:186
#: 312b42dceaa142d5bd0f1a8aad9b8304
msgid ""
"The mechanics are trivial — pass ``-s`` to ``git commit`` and Git appends "
"the line for you:"
msgstr "操作非常简单——向 ``git commit`` 传入 ``-s``\\ ，Git 就会自动为您追加该行："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:193
#: 8d1cc2454b234dafae2886d78e23e9e9
msgid "producing a trailer of the form::"
msgstr "从而生成如下形式的尾注（trailer）："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:197
#: ed5fc5e47c3047b189928d3e01026fcb
msgid ""
"Use your real legal name and an email you control. A pull request whose "
"commits lack a valid ``Signed-off-by`` trailer will not be merged."
msgstr ""
"请使用您的真实法定姓名和一个您能掌控的电子邮箱。如果某个拉取请求的提交缺少有效的 ``Signed-off-by`` 尾注，它将不会被合并。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:201
#: 93a1e174f4ba40abab29f57a458782a0
msgid "If you forget the sign-off on a commit you have already pushed:"
msgstr "如果您在已推送的提交上忘记了签署声明："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:213
#: d48a74911e41436eb5615093c8b872be
msgid ""
"A maintainer cannot sign on your behalf — sign-off is the contributor's own "
"certification."
msgstr "维护者无法代您签署——签署声明是贡献者自身的证明。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:218
#: f4d5757f7efc4560bbd50298c6a84542
msgid "Project layout"
msgstr "项目结构"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:220
#: 5415e27b1b3744c09aa85dd68820013f
msgid "A rough map of where things live, for new contributors:"
msgstr "为新贡献者提供的一份各部分位置的大致地图："

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:226
#: e503297d402143df96bc04b22b56458d
msgid "Path"
msgstr "路径"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:227
#: aa114dd44143446b8b32a70188f8d1ed
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "内容"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:228
#: 0516251c5aed427b8477237bb80f3d19
msgid "``tensormesh/mesh/``"
msgstr "``tensormesh/mesh/``"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:229
#: 694badfa3f0849a9a2ff0a354a6367c8
msgid "``Mesh``, generators (``gen_rectangle``, ``gen_cube``, …), I/O."
msgstr "``Mesh``\\ 、生成器（\\ ``gen_rectangle``\\ 、\\ ``gen_cube`` 等）、输入/输出。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:230
#: 2c2b210c4d85478b9b8b677ac345732d
msgid "``tensormesh/element/``"
msgstr "``tensormesh/element/``"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:231
#: 77d3d65cb979473aa1971645ea22ec5d
msgid ""
"Element types (``Line``, ``Triangle``, …), basis functions, quadrature, "
"Gmsh/VTK reordering."
msgstr "单元类型（\\ ``Line``\\ 、\\ ``Triangle`` 等）、基函数、数值积分、Gmsh/VTK 重排序。"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:233
#: 00f19e7b4f5046cfb699b5343a6c2daa
msgid "``tensormesh/assemble/``"
msgstr "``tensormesh/assemble/``"

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:234
#: d18f3e05d8694d4ba276974597cfe56e
